  "instructions": [
    "In a large pot, heat the olive oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the chopped carrots and celery and cook for 5 minutes.",
    "Add the red lentils, turkish red pepper, salt, and black pepper, and stir well.",
    "Add 4 cups of water and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 30 minutes.",
    "Stir in the dissolved kanten agar and continue to simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh herbs if desired."
